Question 24
Write a PHP script to manipulate the strings with all the string functions.

ANSWER
<?php
$str = "  Hello, World! PHP String Demo.  ";
echo "Length: " . strlen($str) . "\n";
echo "Trimmed: '" . trim($str) . "'\n";
echo "Lowercase: " . strtolower($str) . "\n";
echo "Uppercase: " . strtoupper($str) . "\n";
echo "Position of 'World': " . strpos($str, "World") . "\n";
echo "Substring (7,5): " . substr($str, 7, 5) . "\n";
echo "Replace 'World' with 'Universe': " . str_replace("World", "Universe", $str) . "\n";
echo "Reversed: " . strrev(trim($str)) . "\n";
echo "Shuffled: " . str_shuffle(trim($str)) . "\n";
?>



OUTPUT:
Length: 34
Trimmed: 'Hello, World! PHP String Demo.'
Lowercase:   hello, world! php string demo.  
Uppercase:   HELLO, WORLD! PHP STRING DEMO.  
Position of 'World': 9
Substring (7,5): , Wor
Replace 'World' with 'Universe':   Hello, Universe! PHP String Demo.  
Reversed: .omeD gnirtS PHP !dlroW ,olleH
Shuffled:  l! PSP.tHlo oolirH,gWmD dreen

